data.description: This one owner 3 bed 2 bath one story home is now ready for YOU! Situated in The Meadows in Seguin, it is conveniently located to shopping, restaurants, and recreation. The floorplan is ideal for entertaining with the kitchen being open to both the living and dining areas. The kitchen island has been upgraded with a new large single basin stainless steel sink and faucet that matches with the stainless steel range and built in microwave. The master bath ensuite features a large walk in shower and ample space in the walk in closet.  Out back, a fully fenced yard with extended patio slab and relaxing hot tub. Enjoy walk in closets in every room, separate laundry room, and with ceiling fans and blinds installed, it is move-in ready! New water heater installed 5/10/23.
